---
<section class="py-24 sm:py-32">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-20">
      <div class="mb-6 flex justify-center">
        <span class="ve-eyebrow" data-c="t3">// 06 // Lo que ves</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="ve-title text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-sans font-extrabold leading-[1.1] tracking-tight mb-6" data-c="t3">
        Asi se ve <span class="font-black italic">martes</span> en tu negocio.
      </h2>
      <p class="ve-lead">No dashboards complicados. Paneles simples, en espanol, con la info que necesitas para decidir. Tu equipo aprende en 15 minutos.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-ve-surface border-2 border-ve-border p-8">
        <div class="text-[10px] text-cat-t3 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">// PANEL DE COBRANZA //</div>
        <div class="space-y-3 font-mono text-xs">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-ve-border pb-2">
            <span class="text-ve-text font-bold">Cliente: Distribuidora XYZ</span>
            <span class="text-cat-t1 font-bold">PAGADO</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-ve-border pb-2">
            <span class="text-ve-text font-bold">Cliente: Bodega La Esquina</span>
            <span class="text-yellow-400 font-bold">PENDIENTE</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <span class="text-ve-text font-bold">Cliente: Licoreria 24</span>
            <span class="text-ve-muted font-bold">RECORDATORIO ENVIADO</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-ve-surface border-2 border-ve-border p-8">
        <div class="text-[10px] text-cat-t3 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">// REPORTE SEMANAL //</div>
        <div class="space-y-3 font-mono text-xs">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-ve-border pb-2">
            <span class="text-ve-muted">Ventas:</span>
            <span class="text-ve-text font-bold">$ 12.450</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-ve-border pb-2">
            <span class="text-ve-muted">Cobrado:</span>
            <span class="text-cat-t1 font-bold">$ 9.870 (79%)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <span class="text-ve-muted">Ganancia:</span>
            <span class="text-cat-t2 font-bold">$ 3.200</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
